    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "The project will support to improve municipal infrastructures and governance of the selected project municipalities, thereby contributing to achieve inclusive economic growth and improved livability . This will be achieved through the following three outputs: (i) municipal infrastructure for resilience developed (Output 1); (ii) Tourism assets revitalized and managed (Output 2); and (iii) capacity of municipalities, provinces and Department of Urban Development and Building Construction strengthened (output 3). The project will support seven municipalities (Pokhara, Janakpur, and a cluster of five municipalities includes Devdaha, Lumbini Sanskirtik, Sainamaina. Siddharthanagar, and Tilottama)."
      },
      "ne": null
